The long lost civilization of '''Muror''', located on the legendary lost continent of [[Mu (lost continent)|Mu]], is a mythic civilization invented by [[James Churchward]] (1851-1936). The story was expanded in 1970, in a book published by [[Tony Earl|Tony Earll]]. The book claimed to present a translation of a diary compiled by a boy called Kland. In concept, this myth is not dissimilar to stories and legends about [[Lemuria (continent)|Lemuria]], [[Atlantis]], Mar, [[Thule]] and [[Lumania]].

